#### Estácio de Sá University

Now, to the subject itself. [Estácio de Sá University](/Est%C3%A1cio_de_S%C3%A1_University), also known by its Portuguese moniker, Universidade Estácio de Sá, or the more concise UNESA, is a private institution nestled in the vibrant chaos of [Rio de Janeiro](/Rio_de_Janeiro), Brazil. Its name is a nod to a historical figure, [Estácio de Sá](/Est%C3%A1cio_de_S%C3%A1), a Portuguese knight and military man. This wasn't just any knight; he was the chap who, according to history, founded the very city that now hosts this university. A rather fitting namesake, wouldn't you say? It links the modern educational endeavor to the foundational myths of the region.

